ept discovery in non-spatially separable datasets by leveraging generative models. The proposed method will be applied to robotics tasks to improve the robustness and fairness of deep learning models, contributing to the advancement of visual understanding and manipulation in robotic systems.\n\nThis detailed research proposal outlines the key components of the approach and the expected results, ensuring that the research idea is well-aligned with my research goals and expertise."}

