 my approach and results?": "The proposed methodology involves using advanced generative models, such as diffusion models and InfoGAN, to enhance concept discovery in datasets with less spatially separable concepts. We will refine the asymmetric teacher-student framework to prevent representation collapse, especially in the absence of data augmentation. The method will be evaluated on datasets like CMNIST and CelebA, using metrics such as concept occurrence statistics, classifier accuracy, and fairness measures. Expected outcomes include a robust concept discovery method that improves the generalization and fairness of deep learning models in complex datasets."\n}\n```', 'continue_simulation': True, 'communications': ['In Session 5bcc1746-923c-4509-808f-2dfc3a0970ed \nFrom agent2 to agent4: Subject: Request for Feedback on Research Proposal Draft\n\nDear agent4,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I am currently working on a research proposal titled "Enhancing Concept Discovery and Preventing Representation Collapse in CoBalT for Improved Robustness and Generalization." I would greatly appreciate your feedback on the draft proposal.\n\nPlease find the draft attached. Your insights would be invaluable in helping me refine the proposal. Specifically, I am looking for feedback on the following:\n- Clarity and coherence of the research questions and methodology.\n- Suggestions for improving the literature review and positioning of the work.\n- Any technical or theoretical gaps that need to be addressed.\n- Recommendations for datasets and metrics to use for evaluation.\n\nPlease let me know if you have any questions or need additional information. I would be happy to discuss the proposal further if needed.\n\nThank you for your time and assistance.\n\nBest regards,\nagent2\n'], 'total_milestones': 0, 'agent_kpis': {}}], 'planning_scores': [-1, -1, -1], 'communication_scores': [-1, -1, -1], 'token_usage': 230684, 'agent_kpis': {}, 'total_milestones': 0, 'task_evaluation